"0" videoResolution="720" origin="livetv"/></Video><Video art="https://img.static-ottera.com/prod/tg/media_list/thumbnails/widescreen/3840x2160/recreio-do-jacarelvis-1920x1080_1_3.jpg" guid="plex://movie/696ed0411318078327a28a72" key="/library/metadata/696ed0411318078327a28a72" ratingKey="696ed0411318078327a28a72" summary="Mergulhe em uma série animada pré-escolar cheia de cores, música e aprendizado. A cada episódio, Jacarelvis e seus amigos conduzem os pequenos espectadores por uma jornada divertida e educativa, explorando conceitos como cores, sons de instrumentos musicais e brincadeiras interativas. Prepare-se para se encantar com as aventuras do Jacarelvis e sua turma, enquanto eles ensinam de forma lúdica e cativante." type="movie" contentRating="A" duration="1800000" originallyAvailableAt="2025-10-11T00:00:00Z" requiresConsent="1" skipParent="1" thumb="https://img.static-ottera.com/prod/tg/show/thumbnails/widescreen/2000x2858/recreio-do-jacarelvis-1920x1080.jpg" title="Recreio do Jacarelvis" userState="0" year="2025"><Image alt="Recreio do Jacarelvis" type="coverArt" url="https://img.static-ottera.com/prod/tg/media_list/thumbnails/widescreen/3840x2160/recreio-do-jacarelvis-1920x1080_1_3.jpg"/><Image alt="Recreio do Jacarelvis" type="coverPoster" url="https://img.static-ottera.com/prod/tg/show/thumbnails/widescreen/2000x2858/recreio-do-jacarelvis-1920x1080.jpg"/><Genre filter="genre=6074b802507c8d42cf7e1678" id="6074b802507c8d42cf7e1678" key="/library/sections/home/all?genre=6074b802507c8d42cf7e1678" ratingKey="genre_6074b802507c8d42cf7e1678" slug="kids-family" tag="Kids + Family" type="directory" context="tag.genre"/><Media beginsAt="1775813400" duration="1800000" endsAt="1775815200" id="69d5a55dd9cd0a3327f0b12c" onAir="0" premiere="0" videoResolution="720" origin="livetv"/></Video><Video art="https://img.static-ottera.com/prod/tg/media_list/thumbnails/widescreen/3840x2160/som_da_musica-cover_1920x1080_2.jpg" guid="plex://movie/696ed0411318078327a28a73" key="